---
title: Smart Sweet N' Smoky Glazed Double Turkey Meatballs with Apple, Cucumber and Tomato Salad
description: Cranberry spread and chipotle sauce are the secret ingredients in this succulent turkey meatball meal! Paired with a crunchy apple, cucumber and tomato salad, this is a simple and satisfying smart supper.
